Amanda Holden, 51, shared a series of snaps as she celebrated her friend’s 40th birthday. The Britain’s Got Talent judge wore a daring see-through skirt which showcased her enviable figure. Underneath the garment, Amanda wore a white cut-out swimsuit that was completed with a gold buckle. She smiled as she posed with her friends at the party. In the caption, the Heart FM presenter wrote: “Finally got to do @danielajunepinto 40th.” She also reshared a snap taken by one of her pals that was captioned: “My girls.”